## Important to Know

- CNILâ€™s exemption applies **only to audience measurement**.  
  Combining analytics with **eCommerce tracking, attribution, or profiling** may require consent.

- CNIL released an <a href="https://www.cnil.fr/sites/default/files/2025-07/outil_d_auto-evaluation_mesure_d_audience.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">auto-evaluation tool</a> (July 2025) to verify compliance.

